Package graph.edge

Class SimpleWeightedEdge<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

java.lang.Object
graph.edge.SimpleWeightedEdge<T>
Type Parameters:
T - A generic that extends Comparable
All Implemented Interfaces:
WeightedEdge<T>, java.lang.Comparable<WeightedEdge<T>>
public class SimpleWeightedEdge<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements WeightedEdge<T>
A class that implements the WeightedEdge interface. This class is an implementation of a weighted edge. An instance of this class saves a weight of generic type (that extends Comparable), an integer with the source noce and an int with the destination node. The weight of this edge is not just a Double or float but can be something more complex, as some algorithms might need extra parameters with heuristics.
